<h2>3 · Spot the Bug 🐛</h2>
<p>Read what each block is <strong>supposed</strong> to do, fix it, then explain the fix.</p>
<p><strong>Bug A</strong> — The menu loop should keep running until <code>5</code>. Right now it breaks on <strong>every</strong> choice because <code>break</code> is outside the <code>if</code>.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">while True:
    choice = input(&quot;선택: &quot;).strip()
    if choice == &quot;1&quot;:
        print(&quot;도감 보기&quot;)
    break
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> the <code>break</code> should only run when the user picks quit.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Why was it wrong? Why does your fix work?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Bug B</strong> — <code>main_menu</code> should hand the choice back to the loop. Right now it prints the choice but returns nothing, so the loop never sees it.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">def main_menu():
    print(&quot;1. 도감 보기&quot;)
    print(&quot;2. 종료&quot;)
    choice = input(&quot;선택: &quot;).strip()
    print(choice)

c = main_menu()
if c == &quot;2&quot;:
    print(&quot;종료&quot;)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> <code>return</code> the choice.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Why was it wrong? Why does your fix work?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Bug C</strong> — When the user picks an option that does not exist, the app should say so. Right now unknown input silently loops with no feedback.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">while True:
    choice = input(&quot;선택: &quot;).strip()
    if choice == &quot;1&quot;:
        print(&quot;도감 보기&quot;)
    elif choice == &quot;5&quot;:
        break
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> add an <code>else</code> for anything that is not a valid option.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
